name: STORM ON THE OTTER TRAIL
description: The Otter Trail on the Eastern Cape of South Africa is rated as one of the top multi-day hikes in the world. The weather however is always a bit dodgy being on the southern coast of Africa and exposed to the huge storms of the Southern Indian Ocean. I was setting up camp and watched this storm roll in over the sea. It did mean a rather damp camp that night but I knew I had to capture this image.
